18:52.053 --> 18:54.055
and it's not my fault
you chose meth over teeth!

18:54.139 --> 18:55.515
- Get the fuck out of here...
- Whoa, whoa, whoa!

18:55.598 --> 18:57.600
- You stuck-up bitch!
- [Brook] Oh, my God!

18:57.683 --> 18:59.310
How could you let this happen?

18:59.394 --> 19:01.729
I thought you were supposed
to be about kindness.

19:01.812 --> 19:04.983
You made me think that you care,
but you don't!

19:05.066 --> 19:07.443
And you let a bunch of crazies
speak for you.

19:07.527 --> 19:09.279
Shut the fuck up, Soso!

19:09.362 --> 19:11.614
And you're all just a bunch of
chicken-shit followers!

19:11.697 --> 19:14.117
What? Now I can't help you.

19:14.200 --> 19:16.244
Get out of here, seriously.

19:16.327 --> 19:18.704
Nice group you got here.

19:18.788 --> 19:20.081
Congrats on nothing.

19:26.171 --> 19:27.964
Don't worry.
I'll handle this.

19:42.103 --> 19:44.814
- Which one are you?
- I'm Space Admiral Rodcocker.

19:44.898 --> 19:47.901
It was originally Donaldschlong.

19:47.984 --> 19:50.611
I think I might've made a mistake
by changing it.

19:51.529 --> 19:53.448
I see why you were disturbed.

19:53.531 --> 19:56.367
Yeah, and I don't know how
she knew about my birthmark.

20:01.497 --> 20:03.416
This is some sick stuff, Warren.

20:03.499 --> 20:06.127
A writer does not search out a muse.

20:06.211 --> 20:08.088
