20:22.310 --> 20:25.021
Counselor Berdie Rogers,
she told you to write this?

20:25.105 --> 20:28.649
It was an exercise.
She wanted us to use our imaginations.

20:29.609 --> 20:32.237
Oh, this is the kind of stuff
you do in drama class?

20:33.113 --> 20:35.865
Well, not really.

20:35.949 --> 20:38.034
