a butt-load more time.

21:04.227 --> 21:05.770
- Nope.
- No?

21:05.853 --> 21:08.564
Doggett here don't wanna get out
'cause she'd miss me too much.

21:08.648 --> 21:09.774
Ain't that right, Doggett?

21:12.485 --> 21:13.944
Hey, can you pull in here?

21:17.157 --> 21:19.325
[man speaking indistinctly on PA]

21:30.545 --> 21:32.213
So just like that?
I can go?

21:32.297 --> 21:34.257
That's how it works.

21:35.300 --> 21:36.801
Okay, then.

21:36.884 --> 21:38.428
Peace out, Penn.

21:39.762 --> 21:42.640
I'm sorry about all that shit with Leanne.
I always liked you anyway.

21:42.723 --> 21:43.933
Thanks, Ang.

21:45.726 --> 21:48.104
Hey, ain't your name Sara?

21:48.188 --> 21:49.897
Yeah.

21:52.733 --> 21:56.237
I call her "Ang" 'cause she
reminds me of Angelina Jolie.

21:59.740 --> 22:00.908
Don't you think?

22:01.784 --> 22:03.786
- I don't see it.
- I do.

22:03.869 --> 22:05.746
Whatever. Bye, Sara.

22:06.497 --> 22:08.958
Bye, Penn.
Good luck.

22:11.752 --> 22:14.505
Call the van,
tell 'em to turn around.

22:15.715 --> 22:18.634
What do you mean
they're not answering?

22:18.718 --> 22:20.386
Who is it? Coates?

22:21.929 --> 22:24.849
No, don't call the station.
I'll handle that.

22:24.932 --> 22:27.935
Get a message to Pearson,
tell him I need to see him immediately.

22:28.018 --> 22:29.437
Thank you.

22:31.147 --> 22:34.317
"Sara Rice" has been
dropped at the bus.

22:35.776 --> 22:38.904
Fuck! Fuck!

22:40.072 --> 22:41.491
How does this happen?

22:41.574 --> 22:44.535
The computer assigned her name
to Angie's ID number.

22:44.619 --> 22:48.456
This is MCC's fancy new system.
We gotta call their IT guy.

22:48.539 --> 22:50.958
- Why didn't anyone catch this?
- New COs.

22:51.041 --> 22:55.130
They don't know the inmates,
or, apparently, how to check a photo ID.

22:55.213 --> 22:56.714
It's a huge fuck-up.

22:56.797 --> 22:59.509
This wouldn't have happened
with senior staff.

22:59.592 --> 23:03.888
Christ, I can tell you how many
times a day Flores takes a dump.

23:03.971 --> 23:08.393
I know when Warren is just excited
versus having an episode.

23:08.476 --> 23:11.271
These newbies,
they don't even bother to learn names.

23:14.565 --> 23:16.192
Should we contact the marshals?

23:16.276 --> 23:17.860
No.

23:17.943 --> 23:19.612
Give me a minute.

23:21.071 --> 23:23.908
Maxwell, not a word of this.

23:23.991 --> 23:26.118
You know everybody here.

23:26.202 --> 23:28.746
- Who's in for organized crime?
- Me.

23:28.829 --> 23:31.374
Nah, I need to pick the brain
of a real criminal.

23:31.457 --> 23:34.001
Somebody who's...
more hardcore.

23:34.084 --> 23:36.921
"Hardcore"?
[chuckles]

23:37.004 --> 23:41.551
I worked with the Russian mafia.
We make the Italians look like guppies.

23:42.718 --> 23:45.513
This about your little panty business?

23:45.596 --> 23:48.516
- How do you know about that?
- You recruited my whole family.

23:48.599 --> 23:51.186
They're all running the track
in pink bikinis.

23:51.269 --> 23:53.103
First, you don't ask me to wear them,

23:53.188 --> 23:55.481
and now you undervalue
my criminal mastermind.

23:55.565 --> 23:58.318
You know what?
You really need to go fuck yourself.

23:59.735 --> 24:00.820
I need your advice.

24:00.903 --> 24:03.656
- I want 10% off the top.
- What?

24:05.491 --> 24:07.535
Your girls are rebelling.

24:07.618 --> 24:11.872
You're paying them in sodium and MSG,
and they want real money.

24:11.956 --> 24:13.458
You haven't a clue how to do that.

24:13.541 --> 24:16.961
And as for your one real resource,
your partner,

24:17.044 --> 24:19.797
well, you're fucking around on her.

24:20.881 --> 24:24.885
So it's only a matter of time
before that blows up in your face.

24:24.969 --> 24:27.763
Don't fuck where you eat,
or shit where you fuck.

24:27.847 --> 24:29.682
It's bad business.

24:33.811 --> 24:34.937
Eight percent.

24:40.360 --> 24:42.653
You need to get money
into their commissaries.

24:42.737 --> 24:45.030
And pay your girls a fair wage, huh?

24:45.114 --> 24:46.366
Mmm-hmm.

24:47.408 --> 24:49.744
You know what
Green Dot MoneyPak cards are?

24:49.827 --> 24:52.079
- No.
- No, of course you don't.

24:52.162 --> 24:55.416
They're cash top-up cards.
You're gonna need a cell phone.

24:55.500 --> 24:58.503
- Where am I gonna get a cell phone?
- Oh, the place is crawling with them.

24:58.586 --> 25:00.212
I found one in the bathroom once.

25:00.296 --> 25:01.881
Cell phones are like roaches.

25:01.964 --> 25:03.758
You see one, you'll know
there's another 100

25:03.841 --> 25:05.426
hidden in the walls.
[clicks tongue]

25:06.302 --> 25:07.637
Okay.

25:07.720 --> 25:10.973
Five other inmates in there
with the wrong numbers.

25:11.056 --> 25:13.851
This is the same operating system
we use at all of our prisons.

25:13.934 --> 25:15.853
Yeah, well,
you're lucky you caught it now

25:15.936 --> 25:19.231
- because, clearly, it blows.
- Yeah, this is bad.

25:19.315 --> 25:22.568
This is really bad.
I can't protect you on this one, Joe.

25:24.320 --> 25:26.406
- Me?
- Yeah.

25:26.489 --> 25:30.868
You're in charge of camp.
Shows a big lack of oversight.

25:31.744 --> 25:35.623
[exhales] Yeah... it does.

25:36.999 --> 25:41.379
'Cause the fish
stinks from the head.

25:41.462 --> 25:42.880
And I am not the head.

25:42.963 --> 25:47.092
I am actually
down by the gills somewhere.

25:48.303 --> 25:52.139
So, once I call the police
and the U.S. Marshals,

25:52.222 --> 25:55.184
and the DOC investigators
start sniffing around,

25:55.267 --> 25:57.144
it's going to look a lot worse

25:57.227 --> 26:01.023
for the Director of Human Activity
here at Litchfield.

26:01.106 --> 26:02.858
- Whoa, whoa.
- [mockingly] Whoo, whoa, whoa.

26:02.942 --> 26:04.527
- Yeah, whoa. Slow down.
- Yeah.

26:04.610 --> 26:06.987
Why do we have to involve
all those people in this?

26:07.071 --> 26:09.615
We have an escaped convict!

26:12.034 --> 26:14.203
- Let's just go get her back.
- Who?

26:14.286 --> 26:15.913
You and me.

26:15.996 --> 26:18.999
- Where did they take her?
- The bus station in Utica.

26:19.917 --> 26:23.295
Let's just get in a car.
We'll go get her. Bring her back.

26:23.379 --> 26:25.590
You know, nobody has to know.

26:25.673 --> 26:30.010
So you're saying the two of us should go
and apprehend an escaped convict?

26:31.471 --> 26:34.390
This is not the fucking
Bloodhound Gang, okay?

26:35.558 --> 26:37.393
Well, I don't know what to do.

26:37.477 --> 26:40.062
I honestly don't know
what the fuck to do!

26:40.145 --> 26:41.606
Do you know how I got this job?

26:41.689 --> 26:44.817
My dad is one of the SVPs at MCC.

26:45.526 --> 26:47.194
[scoffs]

26:47.277 --> 26:48.488
Yeah.

26:49.614 --> 26:53.368
This is gonna be worse than
when I got kicked out of Ohio University.

26:54.326 --> 26:57.162
I have no idea what I'm doing.

27:04.462 --> 27:05.671
Fine!

27:07.548 --> 27:09.675
I'll go.
On my own.

27:09.759 --> 27:11.176
Yeah?

27:11.844 --> 27:14.972
Someone needs to stay here
and keep a lid on things.

27:15.055 --> 27:16.306
- Great.
- Fuck it.

27:16.391 --> 27:19.519
If I can get her back,
no one needs to know, all the better.

27:21.353 --> 27:23.188
You're saving my ass, Joe.

27:24.607 --> 27:27.234
Nah... I'm saving my ass.

27:28.235 --> 27:30.738
[men cheering]

27:33.282 --> 27:38.454
Here's to the new opening act
for the East Coast tour of Glass Tiger.

27:38.538 --> 27:40.080
- [Jeff] Hell, yeah!
- All right!

27:40.164 --> 27:41.457
Soon to be the headliners!

27:41.541 --> 27:43.083
- The Jeff Spurber Band!
- Right on.

27:43.167 --> 27:45.335
- We need a new name.
- I like our name.

27:45.420 --> 27:48.130
Of course you like our name,
you're Jeff Spurber.

27:48.213 --> 27:49.757
But you're the tambourine player, dude.

27:49.840 --> 27:51.592
I'm the lead singer.

27:51.676 --> 27:53.678
If we're gonna be named for someone,
it should be me.

27:53.761 --> 27:55.638
- It's my garage.
- [Caputo] Hey!

27:55.721 --> 27:58.766
If Hank and I can get along
after the shit he pulled,

27:58.849 --> 28:00.976
you guys can work it out.

28:02.311 --> 28:05.940
We're looking at ten months
on the road. Let's enjoy it.

28:06.023 --> 28:08.192
Come on,
this is a huge fucking deal for us.

28:08.275 --> 28:10.653
Come on. Come on.

28:12.362 --> 28:14.449
- Lis.
- Hank.

28:18.118 --> 28:20.788
Joey, you got a second?

28:20.871 --> 28:23.207
- Could we talk outside?
- Yeah, babe.

28:23.290 --> 28:25.418
[stammers] Are you sure?

28:27.086 --> 28:28.463
Four months.

28:28.546 --> 28:29.672
So it's...

28:30.840 --> 28:33.092
- it's a real thing...
- [chuckles]

28:33.175 --> 28:34.677
Floating around in there?

28:36.887 --> 28:37.972
How big is it?

28:39.139 --> 28:40.641
Like an avocado.

28:40.725 --> 28:42.435
- Jesus!
- [laughs]

28:42.518 --> 28:43.603
An avocado?

28:44.645 --> 28:47.440
[laughing]

28:47.523 --> 28:48.941
[laughs nervously]

28:49.024 --> 28:51.694
It's great!
It's great.

28:51.777 --> 28:53.488
Lisa, we're gonna have a baby!

28:53.571 --> 28:56.198
- Joey, do the math.
- What?

28:56.281 --> 28:59.660
Four months ago, we were broken up.
I was with Hank.

28:59.744 --> 29:01.704
Four months ago was July.
What are you...

29:07.126 --> 29:09.169
What are you sayin'?

29:12.131 --> 29:13.132
It's his?

29:14.174 --> 29:15.676
Yeah.

29:15.760 --> 29:16.927
Does he know?

29:18.178 --> 29:20.681
I wanted to tell you first.

29:20.765 --> 29:23.851
I've been so guilty about
everything I put you through, and...

29:23.934 --> 29:26.311
now that we're back together, I...

29:27.271 --> 29:29.148
This is so fucked up.

29:30.315 --> 29:31.984
You have every right to hate me.

29:32.067 --> 29:33.986
I love you.

29:34.069 --> 29:36.989
I just thought you should know
because you guys are going on tour and...

29:37.072 --> 29:39.617
I won't go.
I'll stay here.

29:39.700 --> 29:41.702
You have to go!
This is your big break!

29:41.786 --> 29:43.078
That's not why I told you.

29:43.162 --> 29:45.455
Fuck it, they can do it without me.
Fuck it.

29:45.540 --> 29:47.833
Joey, you can't do that.
We'll be fine.

29:47.917 --> 29:49.168
I'm gonna move back in
with my parents.

29:49.251 --> 29:51.003
I already asked for
more shifts at Paddy's.

29:51.086 --> 29:52.630
I'm staying here.

29:53.589 --> 29:56.717
I'm gonna take care of you
and this baby.

29:58.719 --> 30:00.262
I'll tell them right now.

30:00.345 --> 30:02.472
You stay and Hank goes?

30:02.557 --> 30:05.225
Joey, why would you do that?
It makes no sense.

30:05.309 --> 30:06.852
I love you.

30:08.020 --> 30:09.855
I wanna marry you.

30:11.065 --> 30:13.776
I wanna have a family with you.

30:13.859 --> 30:15.444
Hey!

30:15.528 --> 30:16.987
Me and you...

30:18.238 --> 30:19.323
and Avocado.

30:19.406 --> 30:20.741
[laughs]

31:34.982 --> 31:36.233
[sighs]

31:36.316 --> 31:38.402
Aleida's full of shit sometimes,
but I believe her.

31:38.485 --> 31:40.821
I do, too. They said
she tried to chop it off herself.

31:40.905 --> 31:42.239
[Blanca] Hmm.

31:42.322 --> 31:45.034
Oh, I heard she's off her meds
and her penis is growing back.

31:45.117 --> 31:47.828
I heard she was an ultimate fighter
before she turned into a chick.

31:47.912 --> 31:49.454
Well, you heard wrong.

31:49.538 --> 31:54.001
But I will happily go all UFC on your ass
if you keep spreadin' that shit.

31:57.587 --> 31:59.131
Taystee.

32:00.257 --> 32:02.217
Where'd you get that weave, girl?

32:02.301 --> 32:04.679
Don't tell me you went to Danita.

32:04.762 --> 32:07.848
I thought I'd switch it up.
She ain't bad.

32:07.932 --> 32:11.268
Ain't bad? I can see those tracks
from down the hallway.

32:12.645 --> 32:14.730
Look, other people
gotta make a living, too.

32:14.814 --> 32:16.816
My salon has been empty all day.

32:16.899 --> 32:19.652
You think I don't know those Spanish girls
been spreading shit about me?

32:19.735 --> 32:21.195
I don't wanna get involved.

32:22.237 --> 32:24.281
What's wrong with you?

32:24.364 --> 32:25.783
What's wrong with all of you?

32:25.866 --> 32:30.120
Acting like a bunch of stupid,
transphobic bitches!

32:31.496 --> 32:34.208
You know what the worst part of
becoming a woman is?

32:34.291 --> 32:38.170
Having to participate
in this catty, backstabby bullshit!

32:38.253 --> 32:41.841
You don't wanna get your hair done?
You wanna whisper behind my back?

32:41.924 --> 32:45.845
Then fuck you!
Fuck all of you!

32:53.518 --> 32:56.021
- [laughing]
- [sing song] We're in business.

32:56.105 --> 32:58.941
- No way. Whose?
- Mmm-hmm. I've no idea.

32:59.024 --> 33:02.236
There's probably 50 of 'em in here.
This place is crawling with contraband.

33:02.319 --> 33:04.196
You know, I found a blunt,
a lighter,

33:04.279 --> 33:06.741
and a shank made
out of Jolly Ranchers.

33:06.824 --> 33:08.658
Why do you need a phone?

33:10.035 --> 33:11.245
To transfer money.

33:11.328 --> 33:15.332
Each girl is gonna get
a prepaid card on the outside,

33:15.415 --> 33:17.167
give me a 14-digit code,

33:17.251 --> 33:20.838
and then I can wire money
directly into her account

33:20.921 --> 33:23.382
with the touch of a button.

33:23.465 --> 33:24.674
It's called MoneyPak.

33:24.759 --> 33:27.552
Yeah, I know what it's called.
I'm a drug dealer.

33:29.388 --> 33:31.223
Pipes, this is what prison gangs do.

33:31.306 --> 33:34.143
- I know! It's brilliant, right?
- No.

33:34.226 --> 33:35.685
This was a silly distraction,

33:35.770 --> 33:39.148
so we could have some fun
and make a few bucks.

33:39.231 --> 33:43.027
What you're talking about now
is a crime network, okay?

33:43.110 --> 33:45.154
This is the kind of shit
that landed me in here.

33:45.237 --> 33:46.822
So you'll be extra good at it.

33:46.906 --> 33:48.240
Uh-uh.

33:49.241 --> 33:52.702
I'm serious, Pipes. I'm not up for
taking this thing next level.

33:52.787 --> 33:56.706
What happened to that scary, professional
felon I fell in love with, huh?

33:56.791 --> 33:58.667
She was so hot.

33:58.751 --> 34:00.961
Seriously, grow up.

34:04.882 --> 34:08.969
Put one between your knees
and one under your belly. Here.

34:13.014 --> 34:14.433
Why you being so nice?

34:15.684 --> 34:17.018
'Cause I know where you're at.

34:17.101 --> 34:19.063
And, listen...

34:19.146 --> 34:20.981
when your real contractions start...

34:21.065 --> 34:22.858
- Okay.
- You gotta just surrender.

34:22.942 --> 34:26.735
'Cause the more you fight that shit,
the worse it gets.

34:26.821 --> 34:29.072
And it also helps if you moan.

34:29.156 --> 34:31.199
Low, low, like a cow, like...

34:31.283 --> 34:33.118
[moaning deeply]

34:37.081 --> 34:39.208
I don't know why, but something
about opening your throat

34:39.291 --> 34:41.293
makes everything else open up, too.

34:41.376 --> 34:44.670
And pushing feels like shitting,
like you're taking a giant shit.

34:44.754 --> 34:47.800
Ew! That's so gross!

34:47.882 --> 34:49.426
And when they tell you
that they can see the head,

34:49.509 --> 34:51.678
- you got to back off...
- [softly] The head?

34:51.761 --> 34:54.264
And you gotta go slow

34:54.348 --> 34:56.350
so that you don't
tear your shit up, you know?

34:56.433 --> 34:58.685
Stop it, stop it.
I don't even wanna think about that.

34:58.768 --> 35:00.354
I'm just glad everything's
gonna be over soon.

35:00.437 --> 35:01.480
Not really.

35:01.563 --> 35:04.900
You're gonna have a baby
for the rest of your life.

35:08.237 --> 35:10.739
No, I'm giving it away.

35:13.075 --> 35:14.201
What?

35:17.162 --> 35:21.291
- To who?
- To this lady that's been visiting me.

35:21.375 --> 35:24.419
She's really nice,
has a lot of money, and...

35:24.503 --> 35:26.546
my mom thinks I should do it, so...

35:26.630 --> 35:27.714
Aleida?

35:29.799 --> 35:31.385
What are you, fucking crazy?

35:31.468 --> 35:34.304
It ain't right for me to keep a baby
if I'm not gonna be around.

35:34.388 --> 35:35.680
[gasps softly]

35:37.933 --> 35:39.894
So you're saying
I did the wrong thing, huh?

35:41.436 --> 35:43.647
You don't even
get to see her anymore.

35:43.730 --> 35:47.317
Yeah, but at least I know
that she's with her family.

35:47.401 --> 35:50.779
I would give anything to
see my baby for five minutes,

35:50.863 --> 35:54.533
and you're gonna give yours away?
To a stranger?

35:54.616 --> 35:55.825
[scoffs]

35:55.910 --> 35:58.954
You know,
I may be a fucked-up mom,

35:59.038 --> 36:02.332
but at least I didn't sell mine
to the highest bidder.

36:03.333 --> 36:05.335
Yo, give me my fucking pillow back.

36:06.420 --> 36:08.463
I hope she rips you wide open.

36:11.508 --> 36:15.595
